parameters.name: ELECTRON_FLUX_A
parameters.description:
ELECTRON_FLUX_A = (IBS2E / 1.920E+00) + (IIBS2E / 1.920E+00) where   
                        IBS2E  = ^C1.C2.C3.C4.B2.B1.^SB.^G1 and                            
                        IIBS2E = ^C1.C2.C3.C4.B2.B1.^SB.^G1.                               
                        A value of -9.99999e+10 is a missing data value.

parameters.name: STD_DEVIATION_A
parameters.description:
Column contains the statistical error in the associated with         
                        ELECTRON_FLUX_A.

parameters.name: ELECTRON_FLUX_B
parameters.description:
ELECTRON_FLUX_B = (IBS2E / 1.920E 00) + (IIBS2E / 1.920E 00) where   
                        IBS2E  = ^C1.C2.C3.C4.B2.B1.^SB and                                
                        IIBS2E = ^C1.C2.C3.C4.B2.B1.^SB.                                   
                        A value of -9.99999e+10 is a missing data value.

parameters.name: STD_DEVIATION_B
parameters.description:
Column contains the statistical error in the associated with         
                        ELECTRON_FLUX_B.
